h a person perform tarpana with respect to the original family (if they are aware of it)\n&gt;3) What  happens if you are adopted within the family i.e if maternal grandfather adopts his grandson (daughter&#39;s son), then how should the adopted son do tarpana?\n&gt;\n&gt;\n&gt;Thank you.\n&gt;\n&gt;\n&gt;sincerely,\n&gt;Chandraprakash\r\n--673831718-1294167909-1411090925=:16839\r\nContent-Type: text/html; charset=us-ascii\r\n\r\n&lt;html&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:#000; background-color:#fff; font-family:HelveticaNeue, Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida Grande, sans-serif;font-size:10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Namaste friends,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 13px; font-family: HelveticaNeue, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; background-color: transparent;&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 13px; font-family: HelveticaNeue, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; background-color: transparent;&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;If we don&#39;t mention our gotra in a ritual, it is not that gods have no idea. Of course, they know who we are. But, mentioning gotra is just a way of remembering the rishis whose blessings are behind our lineage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div\n style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 13px; font-family: HelveticaNeue, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, &#39;Lucida Grande&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; background-color: transparent;&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;&quot; style=&