se ancestors and other beings when you leave water. Think of them with love and compassion and imagine that they are being freed from the desires. There are formations in our conscious/sub-conscious mind which resonate with various&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;beings of this world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;It is those formations that influence us. Our conscious thoughts modify those formations (and also the external beings through resonance, over time).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;Best regards,&lt;br class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Narasimha&lt;br class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;--------&lt;br\n class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Astrology &amp; Spirituality Resources: &lt;a rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://www.vedicastrologer.org/&quot; class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;http://www.VedicAstrologer.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size:13px;font-family:arial, helvetica, clean, sans-serif;background-color:transparent;font-style:normal;&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;--------&lt;br class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;border-left: 2px solid rgb(16, 16, 255); margin-left: 5px; margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 5px;&quot; class=&quot;&quot;&gt;  &lt;div style=&quot;font-family: Helvetic